| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1932 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7b7ab0b2-6395-5ae6-b493-0451fcf4057d"
